{
  "i18n": true,
  "type": "tabs",
  "items": {
    "general": {
      "type": "panel",
      "label": {
        "en": "General",
        "de": "Allgemein"
      },
      "items": {
        "intro": {
          "type": "staticText",
          "newLine": true,
          "sm": 12,
          "text": {
            "en": "Outgoing messages are sent via open-wa using sendTo(instance, 'send', {to, text}). Incoming replies can either be delivered through the configured state path or via sendTo('reminder.X', 'incoming', payload). Optional wa.me links can be generated so the child or parent can just tap a link and send the prepared reply. For a clean restart without deleting the instance, you can set reminder.0.commands.resetAllRuns to true.",
            "de": "Ausgehende Nachrichten werden über open-wa mit sendTo(instance, 'send', {to, text}) gesendet. Eingehende Antworten können entweder über den konfigurierten State-Pfad oder per sendTo('reminder.X', 'incoming', payload) angeliefert werden. Optional können wa.me-Links erzeugt werden, damit Kind oder Papa nur noch auf einen Link tippen und die vorbereitete Antwort senden müssen. Für einen sauberen Neustart ohne Löschen der Instanz kannst du reminder.0.commands.resetAllRuns auf true setzen."
          }
        },
        "openWaInstance": {
          "type": "instance",
          "adapter": "open-wa",
          "label": {
            "en": "open-wa instance",
            "de": "open-wa Instanz"
          },
          "xs": 12,
          "sm": 12,
          "md": 4
        },
        "incomingStateId": {
          "type": "text",
          "label": {
            "en": "Incoming message state ID",
            "de": "State-ID für eingehende Nachrichten"
          },
          "xs": 12,
          "sm": 12,
          "md": 4
        },
        "replyLinkPhone": {
          "type": "text",
          "label": {
            "en": "WhatsApp number for click-to-reply links",
            "de": "WhatsApp-Nummer für Klick-Antworten"
          },
          "help": {
            "en": "Optional. Enter the number of the WhatsApp account behind open-wa in international format without spaces, for example 491791514520. The adapter will build wa.me links that already contain the reply text.",
            "de": "Optional. Trage die Nummer des WhatsApp-Kontos hinter open-wa im internationalen Format ohne Leerzeichen ein, z. B. 491791514520. Der Adapter baut dann wa.me-Links mit bereits vorbereiteter Antwort."
          },
          "xs": 12,
          "sm": 12,
          "md": 4
        },
        "historyLimit": {
          "type": "number",
          "label": {
            "en": "History entries to keep",
            "de": "Anzahl Historieneinträge"
          },
          "min": 10,
          "max": 1000,
          "xs": 12,
          "sm": 4,
          "md": 3,
          "newLine": true
        },
        "logIncomingMessages": {
          "type": "checkbox",
          "label": {
            "en": "Store last incoming message in info.lastIncoming",
            "de": "Letzte eingehende Nachricht in info.lastIncoming speichern"
          },
          "xs": 12,
          "sm": 8,
          "md": 9
        },
        "participantsHint": {
          "type": "staticText",
          "newLine": true,
          "sm": 12,
          "text": {
            "en": "How to get the WhatsApp IDs: let each person send one short message to the open-wa number. The adapter learns the sender automatically and offers the person in the dropdowns below by name.",
            "de": "So bekommst du die WhatsApp-IDs: Jede Person sendet einmal kurz eine Nachricht an die open-wa-Nummer. Der Adapter lernt den Absender automatisch und bietet die Person danach unten im Dropdown mit Namen an."
          }
        },
        "knownParticipantsPreview": {
          "type": "textSendTo",
          "command": "participantSummary",
          "label": {
            "en": "Learned WhatsApp contacts",
            "de": "Gelernte WhatsApp-Kontakte"
          },
          "container": "text",
          "copyToClipboard": true,
          "xs": 12,
          "sm": 12,
          "md": 12,
          "newLine": true
        }
      }
    },
    "tasksPanel": {
      "type": "panel",
      "label": {
        "en": "Tasks",
        "de": "Aufgaben"
      },
      "items": {
        "tasksHint": {
          "type": "staticText",
          "newLine": true,
          "sm": 12,
          "text": {
            "en": "Each task opens as its own card so the fields are easier to read. For child and parent you can either choose a learned WhatsApp contact from the dropdown or manually type an ID like ...@lid or ...@c.us.",
            "de": "Jede Aufgabe öffnet sich als eigene Karte, damit die Felder besser lesbar sind. Für Kind und Papa kannst du entweder einen gelernten WhatsApp-Kontakt aus dem Dropdown wählen oder manuell eine ID wie ...@lid oder ...@c.us eintragen."
          }
        },
        "tasks": {
          "type": "accordion",
          "sm": 12,
          "clone": "id",
          "titleAttr": "title",
          "items": [
            {
              "type": "checkbox",
              "attr": "enabled",
              "label": {
                "en": "Task active",
                "de": "Aufgabe aktiv"
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 12,
              "md": 3,
              "default": true,
              "newLine": true
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "attr": "id",
              "label": {
                "en": "Internal ID",
                "de": "Interne ID"
              },
              "help": {
                "en": "Use a stable short ID, for example treppe.",
                "de": "Verwende eine stabile kurze ID, z. B. treppe."
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 12,
              "md": 3,
              "default": "task-1"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "attr": "title",
              "label": {
                "en": "Title",
                "de": "Titel"
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 12,
              "md": 6,
              "default": "Treppe absaugen"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "attr": "message",
              "label": {
                "en": "Message text",
                "de": "Nachrichtentext"
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 12,
              "md": 12,
              "default": "Bitte die Treppe absaugen.",
              "minRows": 2,
              "maxRows": 4,
              "newLine": true
            },
            {
              "type": "select",
              "attr": "weekday",
              "label": {
                "en": "Weekday",
                "de": "Wochentag"
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 6,
              "md": 3,
              "default": 3,
              "options": [
                { "label": { "en": "Sunday", "de": "Sonntag" }, "value": 0 },
                { "label": { "en": "Monday", "de": "Montag" }, "value": 1 },
                { "label": { "en": "Tuesday", "de": "Dienstag" }, "value": 2 },
                { "label": { "en": "Wednesday", "de": "Mittwoch" }, "value": 3 },
                { "label": { "en": "Thursday", "de": "Donnerstag" }, "value": 4 },
                { "label": { "en": "Friday", "de": "Freitag" }, "value": 5 },
                { "label": { "en": "Saturday", "de": "Samstag" }, "value": 6 }
              ],
              "newLine": true
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "attr": "time",
              "label": {
                "en": "Time (HH:mm)",
                "de": "Uhrzeit (HH:mm)"
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 6,
              "md": 3,
              "default": "17:00"
            },
            {
              "type": "number",
              "attr": "childReminderHours",
              "label": {
                "en": "Reminder interval child (hours)",
                "de": "Erinnerungsintervall Kind (Stunden)"
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 6,
              "md": 3,
              "default": 3,
              "min": 1,
              "max": 168
            },
            {
              "type": "number",
              "attr": "parentReminderHours",
              "label": {
                "en": "Reminder interval parent (hours)",
                "de": "Erinnerungsintervall Papa (Stunden)"
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 6,
              "md": 3,
              "default": 3,
              "min": 1,
              "max": 168
            },
            {
              "type": "selectSendTo",
              "attr": "childChatId",
              "command": "participantOptions",
              "manual": true,
              "noTranslation": true,
              "label": {
                "en": "Child contact / chat ID",
                "de": "Kind-Kontakt / Chat-ID"
              },
              "help": {
                "en": "Choose a learned WhatsApp contact or type manually, for example 165235998597365@lid.",
                "de": "Wähle einen gelernten WhatsApp-Kontakt oder trage manuell ein, z. B. 165235998597365@lid."
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 12,
              "md": 6,
              "newLine": true,
              "default": ""
            },
            {
              "type": "selectSendTo",
              "attr": "parentChatId",
              "command": "participantOptions",
              "manual": true,
              "noTranslation": true,
              "label": {
                "en": "Parent contact / chat ID",
                "de": "Papa-Kontakt / Chat-ID"
              },
              "help": {
                "en": "Choose a learned WhatsApp contact or type manually.",
                "de": "Wähle einen gelernten WhatsApp-Kontakt oder trage manuell ein."
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 12,
              "md": 6,
              "default": ""
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "attr": "childKeywords",
              "label": {
                "en": "Child keywords",
                "de": "Schlüsselwörter Kind"
              },
              "help": {
                "en": "Comma separated, for example erledigt,fertig,done",
                "de": "Kommagetrennt, z. B. erledigt,fertig,done"
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 12,
              "md": 6,
              "newLine": true,
              "default": "erledigt,fertig,done"
            },
            {
              "type": "text",
              "attr": "parentKeywords",
              "label": {
                "en": "Parent keywords",
                "de": "Schlüsselwörter Papa"
              },
              "help": {
                "en": "Comma separated, for example ja,bestaetigt,bestätigt,ok",
                "de": "Kommagetrennt, z. B. ja,bestaetigt,bestätigt,ok"
              },
              "xs": 12,
              "sm": 12,
              "md": 6,
              "default": "ja,bestaetigt,bestätigt,ok"
            }
          ]
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
